OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FAn exhibition has opened at a pub in
OL,8,FBristol which aims to transport
OL,9,Fcustomers to post-war Britain to see
OL,10,Fwhat life was like for the Windrush
OL,11,Fgeneration.
OL,13,FThe 'Windrush Front Room' has been set
OL,14,Fup in the Shakespeare Tavern to mimic
OL,15,Fhow a a Caribbean home in St Pauls or
OL,16,FEaston may have looked like in the
OL,17,Flate 1950s.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
