OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FHundreds of thousands of people from
OL,8,Fthe Caribbean travelled to Britain
OL,9,Fafter World War Two to help fill a
OL,10,Flabour shortage.
OL,12,FHMT Empire Windrush was the most
OL,13,Ffamous boat to arrive with around
OL,14,F1,000 people from the West Indies in
OL,15,F1948.
OL,17,FBut in Bristol, often, they were not
OL,18,Fwarmly welcomed - having to overcome
OL,19,Fracism, housing discrimination and the
OL,20,Fcolour bar.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
