OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FExhibition curator Tony Fairweather,
OL,8,Fwhose parents are Jamaican, said the
OL,9,FCaribbean front room became a safe
OL,10,Fplace to socialise out of public view.
OL,12,FBut it also was a chance for people to
OL,13,Fshow off what they had achieved and
OL,14,Fpurchased after arriving in England
OL,15,Fwith just a suitcase.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
