OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FTony said: "I wanted to celebrate the
OL,8,Flives of the Windrush generation who
OL,9,Fcame here with just a small suitcase
OL,10,Fand in ten years had property and a
OL,11,Ffront room which have all their prized
OL,12,Fpossessions."
OL,14,F"It's a part of history of previous
OL,15,Fgenerations that's not talked about.
OL,16,FIt was a safe place in the days where
OL,17,Fracism was quite rife, and the safest
OL,18,Fplace to be was in your house and to
OL,19,Fentertain you to take in the front
OL,20,Froom."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
