OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FClassic features of the Caribbean
OL,8,Ffront room included a bar with rum and
OL,9,Fa plastic pineapple, an Axminster
OL,10,Fcarpet, the Blue Spot radiogram
OL,11,Fplaying Nat King Cole and Jim Reeves
OL,12,Fand a glass cabinet of plates that
OL,13,Fwere never used for eating.
OL,15,FTony says this exhibition is about
OL,16,Fcelebrating the way Caribbean and
OL,17,FBritish cultures mixed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
