OL,3,CThe 'Windrush Front Room': Plate
OL,4,Ccollections, plastic pineapples and
OL,5,CJim Reeves
OL,7,FHe added: "They didn't take none of
OL,8,Fthese objects with them on that ship.
OL,9,FThey purchased it all in England. It's
OL,10,Fjust the way Caribbean people put it
OL,11,Ftogether, reflected their lifestyle
OL,12,Fand their heritage that made the
OL,13,FCaribbean front room something
OL,14,Fdifferent - the same, but different."
OL,16,FThe exhibition is touring a number of
OL,17,FGreene King pubs in Bristol,
OL,18,FBirmingham and London over the coming
OL,19,Fweeks.
